name: Respects
author: Injabie3#1660

description: This cog allows users to pay respects, aggregating closely paid respects into one message.
install_msg: Thanks for installing Respects. Use `[p]f` to pay respects, and `[p]setf` to configure other settings.
end_user_data_statement: This cog stores user-defined settings, including their Discord ID in order to associate their preferences.
